            "stanza_text": "Don Rodrigue est à la chasse.\nSans épée et sans cuirasse,\nUn jour d'été, vers midi,\nSous la feuillée et sur l'herbe\nIl s'assied, l'homme superbe,\nDon Rodrigue le hardi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "La haine en feu le dévore.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sombre, il pense au bâtard maure.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "À son neveu Mudarra,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Dont ses complots sanguinaires",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Jadis ont tué les frères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Les sept infants de Lara.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La haine en feu le dévore.\nSombre, il pense au bâtard maure.\nÀ son neveu Mudarra,\nDont ses complots sanguinaires\nJadis ont tué les frères,\nLes sept infants de Lara."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Pour le trouver en campagne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Il traverserait l'Espagne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "De Figuère à Setuval.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "L'un des deux mourrait sans doute.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "En ce moment sur la route",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Il passe un homme à cheval.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour le trouver en campagne,\nIl traverserait l'Espagne\nDe Figuère à Setuval.\nL'un des deux mourrait sans doute.\nEn ce moment sur la route\nIl passe un homme à cheval."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "— Chevalier, chrétien ou maure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Qui dors sous le sycomore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Dieu te guide par la main !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "— Que Dieu répande ses grâces",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Sur toi, l'écuyer qui passes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Qui passes par le chemin !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Chevalier, chrétien ou maure,\nQui dors sous le sycomore,\nDieu te guide par la main !\n— Que Dieu répande ses grâces\nSur toi, l'écuyer qui passes,\nQui passes par le chemin !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
