                    "line_text": "Et la lame est sans étui.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Certe, à moins qu'il ne m'évite,\nJe le reconnaîtrais vite :\nToujours il porte avec lui\nNotre dague de famille ;\nUne agate au pommeau brille,\nEt la lame est sans étui."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Oui, par mon âme chrétienne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "D'une autre main que la mienne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Ce mécréant ne mourra.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "C'est le bonheur que je brigue…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "— On t'appelle don Rodrigue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Don Rodrigue de Lara ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, par mon âme chrétienne,\nD'une autre main que la mienne\nCe mécréant ne mourra.\nC'est le bonheur que je brigue…\n— On t'appelle don Rodrigue,\nDon Rodrigue de Lara ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Eh bien ! Seigneur, le jeune homme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
